  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jon IV</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n336 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 26\">Jon III</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 29\">Arya V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon IV</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_31\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 31\">Jaime IV</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 41\">Jon V</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Climbing_spikes.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/Climbing_spikes.jpg/250px-Climbing_spikes.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"163\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/Climbing_spikes.jpg/375px-Climbing_spikes.jpg 1.5x, /images/8/8d/Climbing_spikes.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Climbing_spikes.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a> climbs <a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">the Wall</a>.<br />© Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> is watching as <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a>’s men are competing with <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">the Magnar</a>’s to see who will reach the top of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> first. Many of the climbers fall to their death, including Jarl, but several eventually reach the top. As long rope ladders are dropped down to the base to allow the others to climb, Jon notices <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> with tears in her eyes. She tells him that they never found the <a href=\"/index.php/Horn_of_Joramun\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Horn of Joramun\">Horn of Joramun</a>, which would have helped them bring the Wall down without a fight.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a> The Magnar</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">The Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Horn_of_Joramun\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Horn of Joramun\">Horn of Joramun</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 7\">Chapter 7</a>, Jon II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/02/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-17\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 17</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2013/10/re-read-jon-iv-messiah-with-ice-pick.html\">Re-read Jon IV: A Messiah with an Ice Pick</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403170659\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.052 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.189 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 328/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9630/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7937/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1066/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 518/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.120/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.38 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  175.285      1 -total\n 98.66%  172.944      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 98.31%  172.330      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 97.87%  171.551      1 Template:Infobox\n  2.45%    4.287      1 Template:Ref\n  1.54%    2.703      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.71%    1.244      1 Template:References\n  0.50%    0.885      2 Template:Columns\n  0.48%    0.845     